text: Keith John Austin Asche, AC, QCOrder of Wearing , Page 5, Note 3. (28 November 1925 - 16 December 2024) was an Australian politician. He was born in Melbourne. He served as Administrator of the Northern Territory from 1993 through 1997. He was the third Chief Justice of the Supreme Court of the Northern Territory serving from 1986 through 1987. Asche was appointed a Knight of the Order of St. John in 1993 and made a Companion of the Order of Australia in 1994. He was made Honorary Freeman of the City of Darwin in 2007. Asche died on 14 December 2024, at the age of 99. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:2024 deaths Category:Administrators of the Northern Territory Category:Australian judges Category:Politicians from Melbourne
